description: A black and white photo of the an excavator construction vehicle on top of a mound of white sand. The main focus is the arm which is parallel to the frame of the image. It starts half way up the frame on the left side where the cab of the excavator is on the sand. The sand tapers off to the lower right side of the image where the bucket of the arm touches the ground turned slightly to where the inner side is visible. The arm is black with "DEERE" written in the middle of it in white letters. The shape of the arm frames a few palm trees in the near background.
